.releases.markdown
  :markdown
    ####  Current Version - 1.4.0 - 2015.10.01

    * Support [C++](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560b4ea6-5a57-4298-84e3-a3057c1ee4b4?fullscreen=true) and [SQL](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560b4a2f-546b-4929-acd7-0d47365b896e?fullscreen=true).
    * Support [Scala Spark](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560cb7e9-68b4-4659-9863-ce5d6ce93dd4?fullscreen=true).
    * Support [IPython widgets](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560d93db-8940-42aa-aeb0-b0fd1af81b3b?fullscreen=true).
    * Support [ggvis](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560ca254-071b-4647-8073-c4f941ca02e8?fullscreen=true) and [bokeh](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560ca17d-b941-4607-8f8e-dd2d5820a131?fullscreen=true).
    * New [publication server](http://pub.beakernotebook.com).
    * Add [EasyForm API](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560ca655-12df-43b9-9ecd-5714766b8fc4?fullscreen=true).
    * Many improvements to the native [time-series plotting API](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1458).
    * New experimental native [Electron builds](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/wiki/Electron-Beaker).
    * Supports IPython 4.0 protocol (except we have a regression of [4.0 and Docker](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2591), so watch for 1.4.1).
    * Consistent use the [Roboto Mono typeface](https://www.google.com/fonts/specimen/Roboto+Mono) for code.
    * [Template expansion](https://pub.beakernotebook.com/#/publications/560b54da-3c14-4890-8b64-b204bc798320?fullscreen=true) in text cells.
    * Improved UI for [inserting cells](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1799#issuecomment-145197219).
    * Improved UI for [hierarchy view](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/470#issuecomment-128892348).
    * New key command to evaluate code line-by-line, or evaluate any selected snippet of code [#2181](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2181).
    * Support for displaying [docstrings](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1501#issuecomment-145198624) in Python.
    * For a complete list of the 341 resolved issues, see [github](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed+closed%3A2015-07-01..2015-10-01).

    ####  1.3.4 - 2015.08.07

    * Fix compatibility with IPython 3.2.1 [#2003](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2003).
    * Fix R outputing graphics and value at the same time [#2020](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/2020).
    * Update Ruby to work with latest version [#1990](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1990).
    * Allow iframes in HTML [#1925](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1925).

    ####  1.3.3 - 2015.07.24

    * Fix IPython in Safari [#1952](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1952).

    ####  1.3.2 - 2015.07.11

    * Fix R in the Docker Container [#1918](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1918).
    
    ####  1.3.1 - 2015.06.26

    * Documentation improvements, especially the dashboard tutorial.
    * Fix tab at beginning of line [#1862](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1862).
    * Fix Scala class loader concurrency bug [#1855](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1855).

    ####  1.3 - 2015.06.26

    * Support PySpark and SparkR [#1521](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1521).
    * Support Clojure and Kdb.
    * Autotranslation improvements such as autodecting date/times, dataframes, images, etc [#522](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/522), [#1412](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1412), [#1522](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1522), [#1525](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1525), [#1664](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1664).
    * New directory for generating files you can access from HTML. [#708](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/708), [#1371](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1371).
    * New editor for text cells and section headers, adding inline math, and fixing bugs with special characters and supporting vim mode [#125](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/125), [#555](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/555), [#704](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/704), [#1315](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1315), [#1345](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1345), [1362](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1362), [#1407](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1407).
    * New data frame interface, including column formatting options [#818](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/818), [#1270](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1270), [#1279](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1279), [#1437](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1437), [#1599](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1599), [#1668](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1668), [#1715](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1715).
    * New insert cell button in advanced mode [#1241](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1241).
    * Restore IRuby [#1129](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1129).
    * IPython handle laptops going to sleep. [#1576](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1576).
    * Allow editing default imports of Python [#1188](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1188).
    * Improved JavaScript stack traces [#889](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/889), [#1357](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1357).
    * Add printing to cell output from JavaScript [#333](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/333).
    * Improved key-bindings, autoindent, and autocomplete [#1365](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1365), [#1467](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1467), [#1468](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1468), [#1505](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1505), [#1649](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1649), [#1661](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1661), [#1670](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1670), [#1773](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1773).
    * Much faster math (TeX) rendering via KaTeX [#698](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/698).
    * Handle very large charts from R [#1540](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1540).
    * Better handling of output from R [#1612](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1612), [#1622](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1622).
    * Improved vertical density, especially of advanced mode [#578](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/578), [#1360](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1360), [#1483](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1483), [#1565](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1565), [#1566](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1566).
    * Increase and improve the included tutorial documentation, and the website [#1400](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1400), [#1528](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1528), [#1604](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1604), [#1642](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1642), [#1775](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1775), [#1784](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1784), [#1785](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1785), [#1833](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1833).
    * Misc UI and layout [#455](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/455), [#569](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/569), [#577](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/577), [#676](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/676), [#1200](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1200) [#1363](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1363), [#1382](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1382), [#1403](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1408), [#1420](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1420), [#1421](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1421), [#1422](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1422), [#1423](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1423), [#1430](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1430), [#1493](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1493), [#1494](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1494), [#1568](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1568), [#1571](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1571), [#1574](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1574), [#1608](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1608), [#1627](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1627), [#1631](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1631), [#1646](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1646), [#1675](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1675), [#1737](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1737), [#1774](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1774), [#1807](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1807).
    * Fixed cookies leak that caused IPython to stop working after extended use [#750](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/750).
    * Add attribution page as required by some licenses [#1733](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1733).
    * Infrastructure improvements like concatenating the JS into fewer files, and upgrading from Java 7 to 8 [#409](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/409), [#897](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/897), [#1229](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1229), [#1384](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1384), [#1388](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1388), [#1445](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1445), [#1463](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1463), [#1600](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1600), [#1619](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1619), [#1703](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1703), [#1734](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1734).
